sequenceDiagram
    participant Index as models-index.yaml<br/>(Local File)
    participant CLI as model-extractor CLI<br/>(Go, CI/CD Time)
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Reg as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS OCI v2
    participant Output as output/*.yaml<br/>(Local Files)
    participant Catalog as models-catalog.yaml<br/>(Local File)
    participant Supp as supplemental-catalog.yaml<br/>(Local File)
    participant Konflux as Konflux Pipeline<br/>(Tekton)
    participant Quay as quay.io/rhoai<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard<br/>(Runtime Consumer)

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Index,Catalog: Flow 1: Model Metadata Extraction Pipeline (CI/CD Time)
        Index->>CLI: Read model definitions<br/>File I/O
        CLI->>HF: GET /api/models/{id}<br/>HTTPS, No Auth (public)
        HF-->>CLI: Model details, collections, READMEs
        CLI->>Reg: Pull OCI manifests & layers<br/>HTTPS OCI v2, Registry credentials
        Reg-->>CLI: Container image layers<br/>(modelcard metadata)
        Note over CLI: Extract model cards from<br/>tar/gzip image layers
        Note over CLI: Enrich metadata with priority:<br/>1. HF YAML frontmatter<br/>2. HF API<br/>3. Modelcard YAML<br/>4. Modelcard regex<br/>5. Generated defaults
        CLI->>Output: Write per-model metadata.yaml<br/>+ enrichment.yaml<br/>File I/O
        Supp->>CLI: Merge static catalog entries<br/>File I/O
        Note over CLI: Deduplicate by model name<br/>Sort deterministically
        CLI->>Catalog: Write unified catalog<br/>File I/O
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Konflux,Quay: Flow 2: Container Image Build (Konflux)
        Note over Konflux: Trigger: git push to rhoai-2.25
        Konflux->>Konflux: Clone repo (git-auth secret)<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP
        Note over Konflux: COPY models-catalog.yaml<br/>COPY models-index.yaml<br/>into ubi9-micro image
        Konflux->>Quay: Push multi-arch image<br/>x86_64, ppc64le, s390x, arm64<br/>HTTPS, Quay credentials
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Dashboard: Flow 3: Runtime Data Consumption
        Note over Dashboard: Mount data container<br/>as volume/sidecar
        Dashboard->>Catalog: Read models-catalog.yaml<br/>Volume mount (File I/O)
        Note over Dashboard: Display validated models<br/>in RHOAI UI
    end
